OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FA "terrified" woman was dragged along
OL,8,Fthe ground for around 150 yards as she
OL,9,Ftried to stop two robbers from driving
OL,10,Foff with her watch.
OL,12,FThe woman, from near in East
OL,13,FYorkshire, grabbed onto the thief's
OL,14,Farm after he stole her watch and was
OL,15,Fdragged along the floor as he fled in
OL,16,Fa car.
OL,18,FWhen he finally let go of her hand,
OL,19,Fshe fell and banged her head on the
OL,20,Fpavement.
