OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FJames Sturman, 20, and Jack Porter,
OL,8,F21, who are both from near Scunthorpe,
OL,9,Fadmitted to robbery after stealing the
OL,10,Fwoman's Apple Watch on 2 February,
OL,11,F2021. Porter also admitted careless
OL,12,Fdriving.
OL,14,FThe woman had advertised the Apple
OL,15,FWatch for sale on Facebook on 30
OL,16,FJanuary and was contacted by several
OL,17,Fpeople, including Porter - who offered
OL,18,Fher #200.
OL,20,FShe said this was too little, but that
OL,21,Fshe would accept #225, heard.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/16
