OL,7,FStephen Welch, prosecuting, said:
OL,8,F"Porter asked if he could come round
OL,9,Fand collect the watch the following
OL,10,Fday."
OL,12,FThe next day at midday, Porter asked
OL,13,Fher if the watch was still available
OL,14,Fand the woman said that it was.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/16
