OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FSturman also sent her a message asking
OL,8,Fif the watch was still available and
OL,9,Fshe told him that it was. She told him
OL,10,Fthat #225 was the best price that she
OL,11,Fcould offer and Sturman said that this
OL,12,Fwas fine but it would take a while for
OL,13,Fhim to travel to her.
OL,15,FShe was already suspicious because of
OL,16,Freceiving messages from both of them
OL,17,Fso close together and because they
OL,18,Fwere written in a very similar way.
OL,19,FShe felt uneasy and kept the watch out
OL,20,Fof the box.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/16
