OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FPorter and Sturman arrived outside her
OL,8,Fhome in a Ford car. Sturman was in the
OL,9,Fpassenger seat and she recognised him
OL,10,Ffrom his Facebook picture. She thought
OL,11,Fthe driver might be Porter.
OL,13,FThe woman handed the box to Sturman
OL,14,Fand the car immediately lurched off.
OL,15,FIt reversed and Sturman apologised,
OL,16,Fsaying: "He's not long passed his
OL,17,Ftest."
OL,19,FSturman reached out of the window for
OL,20,Fthe watch but the woman asked for the
OL,21,Fmoney first.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/16
