OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FShe confirmed that the price was #225
OL,8,Fand Sturman began counting out money
OL,9,Ffrom a wallet and put #20 notes under
OL,10,Fhis leg. He handed the money to her
OL,11,Fbut she told him: "There's only #120
OL,12,Fthere." Two of the notes were fake.
OL,14,FMr Welch told the court: "Sturman
OL,15,Flunged out of the passenger window and
OL,16,Fgrabbed her left hand and wrenched the
OL,17,Fwatch from her grasp."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/16
