OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FPorter began to drive off with Sturman
OL,8,Fstill holding on to the woman. "She
OL,9,Fwas terrified that she was going to
OL,10,Fget seriously hurt or killed," said Mr
OL,11,FWelch.
OL,13,FThe woman was dragged down the road
OL,14,Ffor what she thought was about 150
OL,15,Fyards before Sturman let go of her
OL,16,Fhand.
OL,18,F"As she fell, she banged her head on
OL,19,Fthe ground and she rolled away down
OL,20,Fthe pavement," said Mr Welch.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/16
