OL,7,FSturman was later identified from
OL,8,FFacebook. He made no comment during
OL,9,Fpolice interview. Porter admitted
OL,10,Fgoing with Sturman to the woman's home
OL,11,Fand claimed that he drove off after
OL,12,Fbeing told to do so by Sturman when
OL,13,Fshe grabbed his arm.
