OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FThe woman later said that she had
OL,8,Fpreviously been a confident person and
OL,9,Fdid not really suffer anxiety in her
OL,10,Fday-to-day life, but she had now
OL,11,Fimproved her house security and had
OL,12,Fchanged the locks. She had bought dogs
OL,13,Fto provide extra reassurance and had
OL,14,Fgiven up her job in order to work from
OL,15,Fhome.
OL,17,F"The victim still seems to be
OL,18,Fsuffering substantial psychological
OL,19,Fharm three years later," added Mr
OL,20,FWelch.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/16
