OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FSturman and Porter both had no
OL,8,Fprevious convictions. Nigel Clive,
OL,9,Fmitigating, said that Sturman used
OL,10,Fminimal force during the incident and
OL,11,Fwanted to apologise to the woman.
OL,13,F"This defendant can't turn the clock
OL,14,Fback," said Mr Clive. "He would wish
OL,15,Fto do so.
OL,17,F"This has all the hallmarks of being a
OL,18,Ffraud. He accepts that what he did was
OL,19,Funacceptable. It was a fraud gone
OL,20,Fwrong."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/16
