OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FHe said there was a "cheat level of
OL,8,Fmoney" handed over before Sturman and
OL,9,FPorter drove off, but it seemed
OL,10,Funlikely that the woman was actually
OL,11,Fdragged 150 yards. She suffered a
OL,12,Fscrape and a cut to her knuckles and a
OL,13,Fscrape to her scalp.
OL,15,FSturman had gained qualifications and
OL,16,Fhis dumper truck licence. His
OL,17,Fgirlfriend was due to give birth.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/16
