OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FMichele Stuart-Lofthouse, representing
OL,8,FPorter, said that he had written a
OL,9,Fletter of apology and had shown true
OL,10,Fremorse and exceptional victim
OL,11,Fawareness. She said his actions were
OL,12,Ftruly out of character.
OL,14,F"It was unsophisticated offending
OL,15,Fundertaken by two immature men at the
OL,16,Ftime," said Miss Stuart-Lofthouse.
OL,17,FPorter had previously done a sports
OL,18,Fcourse and was now an apprentice at
OL,19,FBritish Steel, Scunthorpe.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G12/16
