OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,FJudge Tahir Khan KC said: "This wasn't
OL,8,Fa plan to go and rob somebody.
OL,9,FWhatever happened, happened on the
OL,10,Fspur of the moment. If there was any
OL,11,Fcriminal intent, it was most likely to
OL,12,Fbe an offence of dishonesty, possibly
OL,13,Fa fraud rather than a violent offence.
OL,14,FThis wasn't a premeditated robbery."
OL,16,FWhile trying to stop Sturman and
OL,17,FPorter trying to escape with her
OL,18,Fwatch, the woman fell and banged her
OL,19,Fhead as the car driven by Porter drove
OL,20,Foff.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G13/16
