OL,3,CWoman dragged along floor by car in
OL,4,Cbid to stop robbers stealing her Apple
OL,5,CWatch
OL,7,F"I have absolutely no doubt that
OL,8,Fneither of you intended that anybody
OL,9,Fshould be hurt but she was hurt,
OL,10,Falbeit the injuries were not of a
OL,11,Fgravely serious nature," said Judge
OL,12,FKhan.
OL,14,F"Both of you bitterly regret what
OL,15,Fhappened. This is a serious offence."
OL,17,FThey were "very young, naive, immature
OL,18,Fboys" at the time.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G14/16
