OL,7,FSturman and Porter were each given an
OL,8,F18-month suspended custodial sentence
OL,9,Fand 150 hours' unpaid work. Sturman
OL,10,Fwas also given 15 days'
OL,11,Frehabilitation. Porter was given six
OL,12,Fpenalty points on his driving licence.
OL,14,F"This isn't just a let-off," said
OL,15,FJudge Khan. "There is logic in the
OL,16,Fdecision-making of the judge. Losing
OL,17,Fyour good character is a big thing."
